{
  "id": "ai_spring_book_bread",
  "title": "桜木陰のしおり",
  "return": {
    "mode": "town",
    "season": "spring"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "bg": "images/assets/bgev/bg_park_spring.png",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "【思い出ストーリー】桜木陰のしおり",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "外回りの途中、少しだけ時間が空いた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "若葉中央公園も近いし、休憩がてら寄っていくか。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "春の昼下がり。公園には、やわらかな風が吹いていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "桜の花びらが、舗道の上をゆっくり滑っていく。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "木陰のベンチに目を向けると、そこに藍ちゃんが座っていた。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "あ……てんちょー。お疲れさまです。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10201.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "お疲れ、藍ちゃん。こんなところで読書か？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10201.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "はい。ここ、桜の木陰がちょうどよくて……風も気持ちいいんです。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10401.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "藍ちゃんの手元には一冊の文庫本。隣には、パン屋の紙袋が置かれていた。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "昼はもう食べたのか？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "はい、さっき食べました。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10801.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "……でも、素敵なパンが多くて、つい買いすぎてしまって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10701.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "藍ちゃんらしいな。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10701.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "あの、よかったらどうぞ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10401.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "bg": "images/assets/bgev/bg_memory_ai_spring_book_bread_share.png",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "藍ちゃんは紙袋から、桜の形をした淡いピンクのパンを取り出し、こちらへそっと差し出した。",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "いやいや、藍ちゃんが食べたくて買ったパンをもらえないよ。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "……じゃあ、半分こしましょう、私ももう少し食べられますし。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "それなら、ありがたく。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "藍ちゃんは小さくうなずくと、パンを丁寧に分けて半分を店長へ差し出した。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "一口頬張ると桜の香りを思わせるやさしい甘さが、春風と一緒にふわりと広がる。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "bg": "images/assets/bgev/bg_park_spring.png",
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "うまいな、これ。",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "focus-manager",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "ふふ。でしょう？　ここのパン屋さん、最近のお気に入りなんです。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "今度、店の帰りに寄ってみるか。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "はい。てんちょーにも、ぜひ食べてほしいパンがいくつかあります。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10401.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ところで、今はどんな本を読んでるんだ？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "ミステリーです。前作がとても面白かったので、続きが気になってしまって。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ああ、それか。俺も前のは読んだよ。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10501.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "てんちょーも、読んでいたんですか！？",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10601.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "終盤のあの仕掛け、うまかったよな。途中の何気ない会話が、全部伏線になってて。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10601.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "そうなんです。最初はただの描写だと思っていたところが、あとから全部つながって……。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10201.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "読み終わったあと、もう一度最初から読み返したくなるんですよね。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10401.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "分かる。ああいうのは、気づいた瞬間が気持ちいい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10401.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "それからしばらく、二人で本の話をした。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "narration-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "会話が途切れても、気まずさはなかった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "ページをめくる音。遠くで遊ぶ子どもたちの声。桜を揺らす春風。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "ただそれだけで、不思議と満たされた時間だった。"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "……こうやって。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "narration-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ん？"
    },
    {
      "bg": "images/assets/bgev/bg_memory_ai_spring_book_bread_close.png",
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "こういう、静かで穏やかな春の時間が……私は、とても好きなんです。",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear",
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "ああ、そうだな。俺もだ。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "藍ちゃんは少しだけ目を細めて、桜の枝を見上げた。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "cg-clear"
    },
    {
      "bg": "images/assets/bgev/bg_park_spring.png",
      "speaker": "藍",
      "text": "ふふ。それじゃ、そろそろ戻りましょうか。",
      "bgMode": "forceReplace",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10201.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ],
      "forceBackgroundReplace": true
    },
    {
      "speaker": "店長",
      "text": "そうだな。休憩もできたし、戻るか。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/b10201.webp",
          "side": "center",
          "left": "27%",
          "zIndex": 2500,
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "半分こした桜パンの甘さと、藍ちゃんの柔らかな声が、春の記憶として店長の中に残った。",
      "clearStorySprites": true,
      "spriteMode": "narration-clear"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "【思い出アルバムに追加】藍「桜木陰のしおり」"
    }
  ],
